OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FDonald Trump has said the British
OL,7,Fpublic "did not like" Sir Keir
OL,8,FStammer's refusal to be drawn into the
OL,9,Fwar against Iran, as he again derided
OL,10,Fthe outgoing Prime Minister as "not
OL,11,FWinston Churchill".
OL,13,FThe president also repeated his claim
OL,14,Fthat Sir Keir had "hurt himself very,
OL,15,Fvery badly" over his stance on
OL,16,Fimmigration and energy, while
OL,17,Fdeclaring him "a very nice man" and
OL,18,F"sort of a friend of mine".
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@UO]rD@`OUsD@RO]vD@SOUwD@KO]yD@
OL,26,AOOUyD@_O]zD@AOUzD@ZO]
