CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782175667
OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FMr Trump made his comments at the
OL,7,FWhite House after Sir Keir quit as
OL,8,FLabour leader, having acknowledged he
OL,9,Fhad lost the support of his MPs, and
OL,10,Fwith former Greater Manchester mayor
OL,11,Fand new MP Andy Burnham waiting in the
OL,12,Fwings.
OL,14,FThe president has been strongly
OL,15,Fcritical of the Prime Minister after
OL,16,Fhe denied the US use of British
OL,17,Fmilitary bases to conduct the bombing
OL,18,Fcampaign against Iran, although
OL,19,Flimited permission was subsequently
OL,20,Fgranted for defensive strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
