OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FRelations were further strained over
OL,7,Fthe ensuing stand-off in the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz, with Washington berating the
OL,9,Fresponse of the UK and other allies to
OL,10,Fthe Gulf crisis, saying other nations
OL,11,Fneeded the strategic waterway more
OL,12,Fthan the US.
OL,14,FThe White House has been dismissive of
OL,15,FUK and France-led plans for a
OL,16,Fdefensive mission to ensure safe
OL,17,Fpassage for shipping through the
OL,18,Fchannel once hostilities ended.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
