OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FThe conflict only fuelled existing
OL,7,Ftensions over Nato, with Mr Trump
OL,8,Fsaying America had been shouldering
OL,9,Fthe defence of other countries.
OL,11,FOnly last week, US defence secretary
OL,12,FPete Hegseth announced a review of
OL,13,FAmerican military forces in Europe at
OL,14,Fa meeting of the alliance, as he
OL,15,Fcriticised members who "have yet to
OL,16,Fshow a credible path" towards meeting
OL,17,Ftheir spending commitments.
OL,26,@wD@XOUxD@UO]
