OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FHe told his counterparts "some of
OL,7,FNato's largest economies" still seem
OL,8,F"to think the era of free-riding is
OL,9,Fhere".
OL,11,FA row over UK military spending led
OL,12,FJohn Healey to recently quit as
OL,13,Fdefence secretary, piling further
OL,14,Fpressure on the already embattled
OL,15,FPrime Minister.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUoD@YO]pD@AOUqD@EO]
