OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Oval Office, Mr Trump,
OL,7,Fwho is due to meet Nato chief Mark
OL,8,FRutte this week, said: "So we have
OL,9,Fbeen a great member of Nato. In many
OL,10,Fways certainly the predominant member.
OL,11,FWe paid trillions of dollars over the
OL,12,Fyears, not billions, trillions over
OL,13,Fthe years to protect Europe."
OL,15,FReferring to the Iran conflict, the
OL,16,Fpresident added: "We didn't need any
OL,17,Fhelp at all. I was more curious than
OL,18,Fanything else, so I said to Pete
OL,19,F(Hegseth) 'Let's see if they'd
OL,20,Factually come'. So we asked him to
OL,21,Fcome, and they weren't there for us.
OL,26,@pD@XOUuD@]O]xD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
