PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782175667
OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,F"By the way Starmer wasn't there, and
OL,7,Fyou know what, the people of the UK
OL,8,Fdid not like it that he wasn't there.
OL,10,F"Starmer said no. Starmer said worse
OL,11,Fthan no. He said 'We'll be there as
OL,12,Fsoon as you win'. I said 'We don't
OL,13,Fneed you as soon as we win'."
OL,15,FMr Trump went on: "This was not
OL,16,FWinston Churchill we're dealing with.
OL,18,F"As soon as we win, they're going to
OL,19,Fcome and help us."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@]O]wD@SOUzD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
