OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FHe also said Germany and Italy had
OL,7,Fbeen "very bad" over the Iran war, and
OL,8,Fhas had public spats with the leaders
OL,9,Fof both countries.
OL,11,FMr Trump said: "The numbers that we
OL,12,Fspend are so crazy for Nato and they
OL,13,Fweren't there for us."
OL,15,FSaying the US was spending "hundreds
OL,16,Fof millions of dollars to protect them
OL,17,F(members) from Russia mostly", he
OL,18,Fhinted the US may not assist allies in
OL,19,Ffuture.
OL,26,@oD@FOUoD@OO]sD@POUuD@VO]wD@\OUyD@]O]
