OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FThe president said: "We spend all of
OL,7,Fthis money, and then when we want to
OL,8,Fmaybe have help on small stuff ` this
OL,9,Fis small time, this is not the big
OL,10,Fone, this is small potatoes ` they say
OL,11,F'No, we'd rather not help'.
OL,13,F"Stupid thing to say, because we can
OL,14,Fsay that to them if we want, and we
OL,15,Fmight."
OL,17,FMr Trump also had a further swipe at
OL,18,FSir Keir over his immigration and
OL,19,Fenergy policy.
OL,26,@nD@UOUuD@AOUwD@GO]
