OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FHe has repeatedly urged the UK to open
OL,7,Fup the North Sea for oil instead of
OL,8,Frelying on "windmills".
OL,10,FAcknowledging he had been critical of
OL,11,FMr Starmer, Mr Trump said: "I think
OL,12,Fhe's a lovely man, but I said 'You're
OL,13,Freally messing up energy. You have
OL,14,Fwindmills all over the place'. In the
OL,15,Fmeantime, you have the North Sea oil,
OL,16,Fand they won't let anybody drill.
OL,18,F"It's one of the great fields in the
OL,19,Fworld.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@VO]sD@\OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
