SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782175667
OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,F"You know that the UK buys much of its
OL,7,Fenergy, you know where? Norway. You
OL,8,Fknow where they get their oil? The
OL,9,FNorth Sea.
OL,11,F"The UK has a much better portion of
OL,12,Fthe North Sea, they don't want to do
OL,13,Fit for environmental purposes."
OL,15,FThe president added: "He's a very nice
OL,16,Fman, I mean, sort of a friend of mine,
OL,17,FI mean he was not good to us with
OL,18,FNato, Pete (Hegseth), right?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@_O]wD@VOUzD@]O]
