OL,3,CUK 'did not like' Starmer refusing to
OL,4,Cbe drawn into Iran war, says Trump
OL,6,FReferring to Sir Keir's initial
OL,7,Frefusal for the US to use British
OL,8,Fbases, Mr Trump said: "That was a bad
OL,9,Fmove that hurt him badly.
OL,11,F"I wish him well, but he's got two
OL,12,Fproblems ` energy and immigration `
OL,13,Fand crime.
OL,15,F"But energy and immigration. He's
OL,16,Freally hurt himself very, very badly."
